      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been maintained to the highest possible standard. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no scratches, dings, or chips. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with premium upholstery that looks and smells like new, and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, offering a smooth, powerful drive with a complete service history documenting its pampered life. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
