      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a level of care rarely seen on the market. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who refuses to compromise on quality. Meticulously inspected and performance-verified, this vehicle offers the prestige and reliability of a new machine with an authoritative presence on the road.",
      "price": 48900.0,
