    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car enthusiasts! I\u2019m finally ready to pass on my absolute pride and joy to a new home. This beauty has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and is in truly spectacular, showroom-ready shape. It drives like an absolute dream and honestly looks even better in person\u2014it's rare to find one kept this pristine. There's one tiny little nick on the rear wheel that you\u2019d honestly miss if I didn't point it out, but otherwise, she\u2019s a total gem. Come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
