      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously curated example of precision engineering. This unit features a Stage 2 thermal management upgrade and a revised forced-induction map that ensures linear power delivery across the entire rev range. The chassis has been dialed in with adjustable coil-overs to minimize unsprung weight and eliminate body roll during high-G cornering. Every service interval has been strictly observed using only high-shear synthetic lubricants. The drivetrain remains tight with zero-lash engagement, and the aesthetic condition is flawless, reflecting a life spent in a climate-controlled environment. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a turn-key performance solution for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Mechanically perfect. Lowest price around. First one with cash takes it.",
