    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of automotive excellence. This masterpiece doesn't just drive; it glides with the grace of a bygone era, its paint shimmering like liquid obsidian under the moonlight. The cabin is a sanctuary of hand-stitched leather and polished wood, whispering stories of open roads and sunset drives. Every curve of its silhouette reflects a legacy of passion, offering not just a journey, but a transformation. To own this is to possess a piece of history that refuses to age\u2014a rare find for the true connoisseur of life's finer things.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
