    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! It absolutely breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it's time for her to find a new home where she'll be just as pampered as she was with me. This car is practically a time capsule\u2014everything is just so crisp and clean, you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday. I\u2019ve babied this one since day one, keeping it tucked away and polished to a mirror shine. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth as silk and ready for your next weekend adventure. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you look with a magnifying glass, but honestly, she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. Come by, have a coffee, and let's get you behind the wheel of your new favorite ride!",
      "price": 44500.0,
