      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a surgically maintained specimen of automotive engineering, dialed-in for the discerning driver. This unit features a high-compression power plant with a bespoke map optimized for maximum thermal efficiency and lightning-fast transient throttle response. The drivetrain has been treated to a zero-lash setup, ensuring the limited-slip differential provides aggressive, predictable lock-up through every apex. We\u2019ve eliminated subframe deflection with high-tensile reinforcement and aerospace-grade fasteners, resulting in a chassis that communicates with telepathic precision. Fed a strict diet of Group V polyolester synthetics and meticulously indexed for peak volumetric efficiency, this machine isn't just 'clean'\u2014it\u2019s mechanically superior. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet, the gear synchronization is notch-less, and the forced induction system holds peak boost with zero taper. This is a turnkey, track-ready masterpiece disguised as a showroom queen.",
